          <title>
            <string language="en">Higher Level Exam Technique</string>
            <string language="es">Técnica para el examen del nivel superior</string>
            <string language="ga">Teicníc don Scrúdú Ardleibhéil</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Höhere Stufe Prüfung-Technik</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Technique d'Examen de Niveau Plus élevé</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Técnica Do Exam Do Nível Mais elevado</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Tecnica Del Exam Del Livello elevato</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Τεχνική διαγωνισμών πιό υψηλού επιπέδου</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">Details of a structured approach to tackling the Higher Level paper with a five-step approach outlined. Questions and suggested solutions are provided.</string>
            <string language="es">Detalles de una metodología estructurada para abordar el examen de nivel superior con un esquema de metodología de cinco pasos. Se incluyen preguntas y soluciones sugeridas.</string>
            <string language="ga">Sonraí maidir le cur chuige struchtúrtha le dul i ngleic leis an bpáipéar Ardleibhéil le himlíniú ar chur chuige cúig chéim. Cuirtear ceisteanna agus freagraí molta ar fáil.</string>
          </description>
          <language>en</language>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Business</string>
            <string language="es">Empresariales</string>
            <string language="ga">Gnó</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Additional Resource</string>
            <string language="es">Recurso adicional</string>
            <string language="ga">Acmhainn Bhreise</string>
          </keyword>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Details einer strukturierten Annäherung an das 
Anpacken des höhere Stufe Papiers mit einem Fünfjobstep nähern sich
umrissen. Fragen und vorgeschlagene Lösungen werden zur 
Verfügung gestellt.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les détails d'une approche structurée à 
aborder le papier de niveau plus élevé avec une cinq-étape 
s'approchent tracé les grandes lignes. Des questions et les 
solutions suggérées sont fournies.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Os detalhes de uma aproximação estruturada a 
tackling o papel de um nível mais elevado com uma cinco-etapa 
aproximam-se esboçado. As perguntas e as soluções sugeridas 
são fornecidas.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">I particolari di un metodo strutturato ad 
affrontare la carta dal livello elevato con un cinque-punto si 
avvicinano a descritto. Le domande e le soluzioni suggerite sono
fornite.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Οι λεπτομέρειες μιας δομημένης προσέγγισης στην 
αντιμετώπιση του εγγράφου πιό υψηλού επιπέδου με ένα 
πέντε-βήμα πλησιάζουν περιγραμμένος. Οι ερωτήσεις και οι 
προτεινόμενες λύσεις παρέχονται.</string>
          </description>
